KCTRONICS Presigned URL Helper
==============================

Usage:
1. Ensure AWS CLI credentials are configured or AWS_PROFILE exported.
2. Install boto3 if not installed:
   python3 -m pip install --user boto3
3. Run:
   python3 create_presigned_url.py --bucket your-bucket --key kctronics_monitoring_dashboard_v1.zip --expires 86400
4. Copy the generated HTTPS URL into your ec2_user_data.sh as:
   MONITORING_S3_URL="<your generated URL>"

IAM permissions required:
- s3:GetObject for the specific S3 object (or Put/List if also uploading).
